723298f-a.text:
South Street, under the Brooklyn Bridge, showing several warehouses that face the East River, and from which the photographer is viewing. These bear No's. 168-70 South Street. They
are between Dover and Roosevelt Street's.
October 1927
George L. Balgue, photo
723298f-a.folder: South Street & Dover Street, Manhattan, NY

719332f-a.text:
Dover Street, north side, west from South Street. This view also shows South Street, west side, at Dover Street.
May 3, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
719332f-a.folder: Dover Street & South Street, Manhattan, NY
